::Feline::

She followed behind them and watched.  She walked and smiled.  She 
thought she had brought Zardus a prize by bringing him HotRod and 
CyberShark.  Battera wasn't much of a prize, but would at least be 
another fighter for Zardus.  She has now completed her mission, and 
wanted to see if Zardus would repay her well for her efforts.
